# Asymmetric Cryptography Visual Demonstration

Here's a beautifully designed, self-contained HTML file that visually demonstrates asymmetric cryptography with exceptional aesthetics:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Asymmetric Cryptography | Visual Journey</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #6c5ce7;
            --secondary: #a29bfe;
            --accent: #fd79a8;
            --dark: #2d3436;
            --light: #f5f6fa;
            --success: #00b894;
            --warning: #fdcb6e;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            color: var(--dark);
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-out;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--accent));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--dark);
            opacity: 0.8;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .visualization {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4rem;
            margin-top: 4rem;
        }

        .key-pair {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 4rem;
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
        }

        .key {
            width: 280px;
            height: 380px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .key:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 30px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .public-key {
            border-top: 8px solid var(--primary);
        }

        .private-key {
            border-top: 8px solid var(--accent);
        }

        .key-icon {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: white;
        }

        .public-key .key-icon {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.3);
        }

        .private-key .key-icon {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #ff7675);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(253, 121, 168, 0.3);
        }

        .key-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .key-description {
            text-align: center;
            color: #636e72;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .key-value {
            background: var(--light);
            padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            word-break: break-all;
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: auto;
            border: 1px solid #dfe6e9;
        }

        .connection-line {
            position: absolute;
            height: 4px;
            width: 200px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--accent));
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            z-index: 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .process-flow {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 4rem;
        }

        .flow-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .flow-steps {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 2rem;
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
        }

        .step {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            width: 200px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            position: relative;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
        }

        .step:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .step-number {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .step-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--dark);
        }

        .step-description {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #636e72;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .arrow {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }

        .arrow-left {
            left: -20px;
        }

        .arrow-right {
            right: -20px;
        }

        .demo-section {
            margin-top: 6rem;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 3rem;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .demo-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--accent));
        }

        .demo-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .demo-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 3rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .message-box {
            width: 300px;
            background: var(--light);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .message-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--dark);
            text-align: center;
        }

        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            height: 120px;
            border: 1px solid #dfe6e9;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 0.8rem;
            font-family: inherit;
            resize: none;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.2);
        }

        .btn {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.3);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #5a4bd1;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.4);
        }

        .btn:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .encrypted-message {
            background: rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.1);
            border: 1px dashed var(--primary);
        }

        .decrypted-message {
            background: rgba(253, 121, 168, 0.1);
            border: 1px dashed var(--accent);
        }

        .status {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #636e72;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .visual-animation {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            position: relative;
            margin: 3rem 0;
        }

        .animation-container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .animation-node {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            position: absolute;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.5s ease;
        }

        .sender {
            background: var(--primary);
            left: 20%;
        }

        .receiver {
            background: var(--accent);
            right: 20%;
        }

        .message {
            background: var(--success);
            top: 30%;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .encrypted-message-anim {
            background: var(--warning);
            top: 30%;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .public-key-anim {
            background: var(--secondary);
            top: 70%;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .private-key-anim {
            background: #ff7675;
            top: 70%;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .animation-path {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 20%;
            width: 60%;
            height: 2px;
            background: #dfe6e9;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .animation-path::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -100px;
            left: 50%;
            width: 2px;
            height: 100px;
            background: #dfe6e9;
        }

        .animation-controls {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .animate-btn {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.3);
        }

        .animate-btn:hover {
            background: #5a4bd1;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.4);
        }

        .animate-btn:disabled {
            background: #b2bec3;
            cursor: not-allowed;
            transform: none;
            box-shadow: none;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 6rem;
            padding: 2rem 0;
            color: #636e72;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
        }

        .floating {
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .pulsing {
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .key-pair {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 2rem;
            }

            .connection-line {
                width: 4px;
                height: 100px;
                left: 50%;
                top: auto;
                bottom: -50px;
                transform: translate(-50%, 0);
            }

            .flow-steps {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 3rem;
            }

            .step {
                width: 80%;
            }

            .arrow {
                top: auto;
                left: 50%;
                transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(90deg);
            }

            .arrow-left {
                top: -20px;
            }

            .arrow-right {
                top: calc(100% + 20px);
            }

            .demo-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .sender {
                left: 10%;
            }

            .receiver {
                right: 10%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Asymmetric Cryptography</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">A visual journey through public-key cryptography, where security meets elegance through mathematically linked key pairs.</p>
        </header>

        <div class="visualization">
            <div class="key-pair">
                <div class="key public-key floating">
                    <div class="key-icon">🔑</div>
                    <h3 class="key-title">Public Key</h3>
                    <p class="key-description">Shared openly with anyone who needs to send you encrypted messages or verify your signatures.</p>
                    <div class="key-value">04a8b9c3d2e1f0a9b8...c7d6e5f4a3b2c1d0e9f8</div>
                </div>

                <div class="connection-line"></div>

                <div class="key private-key floating" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
                    <div class="key-icon">🔒</div>
                    <h3 class="key-title">Private Key</h3>
                    <p class="key-description">Kept secret at all times. Used to decrypt messages or create digital signatures.</p>
                    <div class="key-value">1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c...0d9e8f7a6b5c4d3e2f1a</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="process-flow">
                <h2 class="flow-title">The Encryption Process</h2>

                <div class="flow-steps">
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">1</div>
                        <h4 class="step-title">Key Generation</h4>
                        <p class="step-description">Mathematically linked public and private keys are created using complex algorithms.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="arrow arrow-right">→</div>

                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">2</div>
                        <h4 class="step-title">Public Distribution</h4>
                        <p class="step-description">The public key is shared openly while the private key remains securely stored.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="arrow arrow-right">→</div>

                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">3</div>
                        <h4 class="step-title">Encryption</h4>
                        <p class="step-description">Anyone can encrypt data using the public key, but only the private key can decrypt it.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="arrow arrow-right">→</div>

                    <div
